com.github.nosan.embedded.cassandra.configuration

Interface TransparentDataEncryptionOptions.Builder

  • Enclosing interface:
    TransparentDataEncryptionOptions

    public static interface TransparentDataEncryptionOptions.Builder
    Builds instances of type TransparentDataEncryptionOptions. Initialize attributes and then invoke the build() method to create an instance.

    TransparentDataEncryptionOptionsBuilder is not thread-safe and generally should not be stored in a field or collection, but instead used immediately to create instances.

    Author:
    Dmytro Nosan
